						               													<description>Grand Sumo is a 2-player card game based on the 1,500 year old sport of sumo wrestling, in which you will be programming your wrestler&amp;rsquo;s actions through card play and aim to either push you opponent out of the ring, or wrestle him to the ground.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Like real sumo bouts, you can attempt to attack aggressively in hope of a quick victory, or try to outwit and outlast your opponent.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each bout in Grand Sumo consists of 3 contacts, where you will simultaneously program your wrestlers' actions by playing cards face down in front of you. When both players are ready, the cards are revealed one at a time, and resolved as pushing, wrestling and defensive actions in the ring.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who manages to push or rotate the wrestlers token to meet a winning condition wins the bout, and the first player to win 3 bouts will be crowned the winner of Grand Sumo.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
